HEADWORD: male body
<hw>male body</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The body of an adult human male;
-- a term used especially in art; <as>as, <person>Da Vinci</person> was
unexcelled in painting the <ex>male body</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> adult male body, man's body.</syn>⟦br⟧
